Battlefish is an American reality television show that follows the pursuits of several fishing boats as they search the Pacific Ocean for albacore tuna. The eight-episode first season debuted on Netflix on the 21st of September, 2018. The show is produced by Pilgrim Media Group.
The series documents five fishing crews along the coasts of Washington and Oregon during the 2017 fishing season.
